# Visual System

- Aim for a game-like viewing surface with intentional typography, color, and motion.
- Decorative effects must not reduce legibility of rankings, progress, or alerts.
- Use spacing and contrast to make race state changes readable faster than body copy.
- Prefer a coherent visual direction over one-off flourishes.
